53
00:03:23,270 --> 00:03:26,770
I told you I didn't mean anything by it.

54
00:03:27,770 --> 00:03:29,670
It's nothing at all.

55
00:03:31,070 --> 00:03:34,780
The Yu Seongbin I know wouldn't say

56
