57
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:38,550
Tell me.

58
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:40,620
It's really nothing at all.

59
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:42,320
I didn't mean anything by it.

60
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,790
Seongbin.

61
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:49,520
Tell me why you said that.

62
00:03:53,230 --> 00:03:54,800
Seongbin!

63
