Where did you hear it from?

72
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,400
Well...

73
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,860
No, forget it.

74
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:28,530
I'm sure it was a misunderstanding.

75
00:04:28,530 --> 00:04:30,400
I was just worried about you.

76
00:04:31,170 --> 00:04:34,000
Don't worry. I trust my husband.

77
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,770
He would never cheat on me.

78
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:39,010
Seongbin.

79
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:42,340
