102
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:55,850
Or the day of his death.

103
00:05:57,820 --> 00:06:00,490
I didn't mean to forget.

104
00:06:00,490 --> 00:06:02,320
I just forgot naturally.

105
00:06:04,290 --> 00:06:08,160
I had loved him so much, but I started to forget.

106
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:16,800
