121
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:16,360
Shh! You'll wake up the family.

122
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:29,240
I went to your shop to treat you to dinner.

123
00:08:31,610 --> 00:08:35,810
What is that on your chest?

124
00:08:35,810 --> 00:08:37,180
Is it a diamond?

125
00:08:38,610 --> 00:08:40,580
Diamond?

126
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:42,080
It was a gift.

127
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,850
A gift? From whom?

128
00:08:44,850 --> 00:08:46,250
A friend.

129
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:50,160
Are you talking about Mr. Yu

130
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:52,660
who works at your father's firm?

131
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:57,470
You're lucky to get a gift from a guy.

132
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,930
Yes, I'm lucky.

133
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:02,400
Stop meeting with him.

134
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:05,310
Now that you're married, stop seeing him.

135
00:09:05,310 --> 00:09:08,080
But Seongbin and I go way back.

136
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,440
Whatever!

137
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,830
Hello?

138
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:27,100
It's me.

139
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:36,340
Why couldn't I reach you?

140
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:40,310
<i>Why? Did you miss me?</i>

141
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:42,580
<i>Tell me that you missed me.</i>

142
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:44,980
<i>Then I'll go see you right away.</i>

143
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:48,250
Oh, really?

144
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:54,490
It's a little late.

145
00:09:54,490 --> 00:09:55,790
See you tomorrow.

146
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:05,930
Jinwu, say "Ah".

147
00:10:05,930 --> 00:10:08,770
No, I want my mom to feed me.

148
00:10:08,770 --> 00:10:10,770
Okay, Jinwu. Here you go.

149
00:10:10,770 --> 00:10:13,640
You should eat well to grow up strong.

150
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,940
That's good.

151
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:19,050
Why did you get home so late last night?

152
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:22,880
I'm sorry, mother. I had an appointment.

153
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:24,650
You're a mother.

154
00:10:24,650 --> 00:10:27,620
You should've come home early.

155
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,620
Come on, mom.

156
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:31,060
You didn't say anything

157
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:32,330
