158
00:10:32,330 --> 00:10:33,860
Be quiet.

159
00:10:33,860 --> 00:10:36,530
Men and women are different.

160
00:10:36,530 --> 00:10:37,780
Yeonhui works, too.

161
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:39,540
What are you saying?

162
