165
00:10:45,970 --> 00:10:47,940
Jeong Yumi, stop it.

166
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:49,610
If you keep that up...

167
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,110
Byeongguk.

168
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,420
How is the deal With Lasar going?

169
