172
00:11:02,990 --> 00:11:05,830
Who is Grace Lee?

173
00:11:06,830 --> 00:11:07,830
Huh?

174
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:12,130
The Lasar assistant manager from the States.

175
00:11:12,130 --> 00:11:13,670
You should take more interest

176
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:15,070
