181
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,750
Why are they stalling?

182
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,250
I'm so nervous.

183
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:36,360
Byeongguk?

184
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,730
What happened to the deal with Lasar?

185
00:11:38,730 --> 00:11:40,630
