186
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,960
It will go well.

187
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:44,430
So why is it taking so long?

188
00:11:44,430 --> 00:11:46,100
I'm going mad.

189
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:49,500
It'll be over soon.

190
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:51,310
It'll go well.

