00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:59,150
<i>It'll go well</i>

192
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:09,120
<i>Do you know Grace Lee?</i>

193
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:12,090
<i>Byeongguk.</i>

194
00:12:12,090 --> 00:12:15,030
<i>How is the deal with Lasar going?</i>

195
00:12:15,030 --> 00:12:17,800
<i>Grace Lee still hasn't made a decision?</i>

196
00:12:19,330 --> 00:12:21,070
Grace Lee?

