208
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:03,910
Honey?

209
00:13:04,610 --> 00:13:07,150
Do you have any spicy soup?

210
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:09,520
My stomach hurts and my mouth feels dry.

211
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:12,350
That's why I've made some bean sprout soup.

212
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:15,920
You shouldn't have drunk so much.

213
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:17,120
Where is Junhui?

214
00:13:17,130 --> 00:13:19,790
She’s sick. She can't go to work today.

215
00:13:20,530 --> 00:13:21,930
