216
00:13:21,930 --> 00:13:25,370
She's been sick with a cold since last night.

217
00:13:25,370 --> 00:13:26,430
Really?

218
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:45,650
It's me. Can I come in?

219
00:13:45,650 --> 00:13:46,720
Come in.

220
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:53,130
What's wrong? You're not well?

221
00:13:53,130 --> 00:13:54,300
It's not a big deal.

222
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:58,970
You don't have a fever.

223
00:13:58,970 --> 00:14:00,630
