224
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:03,100
But I don't think I can go to work.

225
00:14:03,110 --> 00:14:07,070
If you're sick, you should take the day off.

226
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,680
Call me later.

227
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:09,910
Dad?

228
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:15,580
Do you think I should go overseas to study?

229
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:19,320
Why would you say that out of the blue?

230
00:14:20,060 --> 00:14:21,760
Why?

231
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:25,330
Because Yunmi studied overseas,
do you think you're falling behind?

232
00:14:25,330 --> 00:14:27,190
You studied overseas, too.

233
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,760
That was then.

234
00:14:29,900 --> 00:14:32,400
You're talented.

235
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:34,070
I'm not saying this as your dad

236
00:14:34,070 --> 00:14:36,240
